incident_updates.body: We have identified the root cause at 14:46 UTC. The error rate is decreasing.
We are continuing to investigate this issue.

Start time : 09/02/2024 11:10 UTC Service impact : Customers can have disconnection and 500/503 errors visible to customers. Ongoing actions : Investigating. Our technical teams are working on the issue. Update will be posted as significant progress is made.

Start time : 09/01/2024 16:10 UTC End time : 09/01/2024 17:10 UTC Service impact : None Service improvement : As part of our continuous improvement policy of our network infrastructure, we will have to carry out interventions on a network equipment.
